{"tid":413498,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"香港首屆健美小姐冠軍馬清儀 癌症離世","createTime":"2017-09-25T13:05:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T13:05:45.000Z","uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dcafc49576d7003deb3b1125847cf541d3cb2ea2","tid":413498,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/25/210539_248713bdd84604abbb101aca101ea89c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F25%2F210539_248713bdd84604abbb101aca101ea89c.jpg&h=a5d14a08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬清儀為無線電視於1985年舉辦的首屆健美小姐比賽的冠軍得主，於9月7日因病離世，終年64歲。同年參選的更有藝人梅小惠，而馬清儀於得獎同年亦跟無線電視簽約，成為旗下藝人。當年的賽果曾被懷疑造假，皆因其「富二代」的身份，及後更被亞軍公開質疑大會不公，引起公眾嘩然，但馬清儀選擇回應有關造馬的言論，並對賽果表示「問心無愧」，顯示出她化解傳言的能力與大方性格。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2xA4B3W\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2xA4B3W&d=Hyb4F1R1nV3agLD70oOVjkjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=4c036334\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2xA4B3W</a>"}]}